description: Structured renewal management command center that surfaces upcoming renewals, risk levels, expansion potential, and required actions across 90/60/30-day windows. A CSM agent and a Workflow agent replace the manual renewal tracker spreadsheets, Gainsight notes, and quarterly renewal fire drills. Every renewal has an action plan on disk.
